{"tid":2105863,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美國商會：30%商會成員考慮中長期撤資或將業務遷離香港","createTime":"2020-07-13T02:40:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-13T05:27:44.000Z","uid":79563,"like":50,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"b83aca120f2a7624365449a79cdf818b0603bf38","tid":2105863,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T02:40:55.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1537397-20200713.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1537397-20200713.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=Z5C23SoLFrdwUrTWaDZos5riIWEbfV0cuvPRs67P9cA%3D&h=dd1e186b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1537397-20200713.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=d886d1ef\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1537397-20200713.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n香港美國商會一項調查顯示，近49%受訪者認為「港區國安法」對生意帶來負面影響。30%受訪者表示，考慮中長期撤資或把業務遷離香港，約有5.5%受訪者則考慮短期撤資。<br />\n<br />\n調查在本月6日至8日進行，收集到183名成員回覆，佔總數15%。當中，41%人極度關注「港區國安法」，主要憂慮法例覆蓋範圍和執法模糊、影響香港司法獨立，以及削弱本港金融中心地位等。56%人認為已公布條文比預期中嚴苛，擔心域外管轄權、引渡中國，「與外國勢力勾結」條文等問題。<br />\n<br />\n調查同時顯示，51%人認為法例實施後在港工作和生活更不安全，41%人對香港前景感到悲觀。"},{"pid":"9adbe2ab6e294764a491748cdf723e0ca4dab659","tid":2105863,"uid":8880,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T02:42:02.000Z","msg":"仲有70%美奸"},{"pid":"b7d50ded0abff90acd6d3aa12e2764e3bcb62f2d","tid":2105863,"uid":159448,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T02:43:10.000Z","msg":"中長期係10-20年？"},{"pid":"f8aa8a9f41a1fbbb3fee98a65530d49b3cfc4de3","tid":2105863,"uid":79563,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T02:43:14.000Z","msg":"美國商會應該真係收到白宮既風"},{"pid":"1aa8f641392b4c3c201a66f8f8f9867ab75a71e4","tid":2105863,"uid":68080,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T02:43:30.000Z","msg":"一條國安法就35.5%想走啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gi